The following files incorporate structural patterns and several
non-negotiable rules from ForgeCode's agent system prompts:

  - pkg/agent/prompts/shared_header.md
  - pkg/agent/prompts/ask.md
  - pkg/agent/prompts/plan.md
  - pkg/agent/prompts/do.md

The three-mode decomposition (ask/plan/do) corresponds to ForgeCode's
built-in "sage" (read-only research), "muse" (planning), and "forge"
(implementation) agent roles.

See pkg/agent/prompts/UPSTREAM.md for details on what was borrowed,
where we diverge, and re-sync cadence.

